The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Clay best for return: Sania

New Delhi: Sania Mirza believes that clay although not her favourite surface will be the ideal platform for her to make a comeback after a knee injury. Clay is the best surface for me to start playing again after the knee injury. My trainer Heath Matthews also feels, Sania said from Hyderabad. 

Sanis left Sunday for Morocco where she will return to action at a $145,000 WTA Tour event. (PTI) 




